# Design System & Theme

## Colors & Typography
- **No hardcoded colors**: Use `AppTheme` from [lib/app/utils/theme.dart](mdc:lib/app/utils/theme.dart)
- **Typography**: Use predefined styles like `AppTheme.headlineLarge`, `AppTheme.bodyLarge`
- **Color palette**: Bumble yellows, accent orange/blue/green, status colors

## Cards & Components
- **Border radius**: 16px • **Shadow**: Use `AppTheme.cardShadow`
- **Property cards**: Hero image with gradient overlay and bottom info panel
- **Spacing**: Use consistent values (8/12/16/24) • Avoid magic numbers

## States & Components
- **Loading/Error UI**: Use shared widgets from `lib/widgets/common/`
- **Reference components**:
  - Bottom nav: [lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/navigation/bottom_nav_bar.dart)
  - Property cards: [lib/app/modules/home/widgets/property_swipe_card.dart](mdc:lib/app/modules/home/widgets/property_swipe_card.dart)

## Do Not
- Hardcode `Colors.*` or font sizes
- Use inconsistent radii or shadows
- Create duplicate components